{"word":"Miriam","slug":"miriam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Miriam</b> - sister of Moses<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=4'>Exo 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=20'>Exo 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=10'>Num 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=15'>Num 12:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=1'>Num 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=9'>Deu 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=4'>Mic 6:4</a><p/>-- \"The Ambitious Woman\"<p/>Characteristics of<p/>Alert in youth<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=7'>Ex 2:7</a><p/>Vigorous and musical in later years<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=21'>Ex 15:21</a><p/>Ambitious<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=2'>Num 12:2</a><p/>Regarded as a leader in Israel<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=4'>Mic 6:4</a>"}]}